Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.87,0:01:51.89,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,0)}失控
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.71,0:00:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙  为什么会在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.82,0:00:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了什么而生下来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.18,0:00:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我  回答我啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.94,0:02:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶梦…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.48,0:02:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确是亲眼看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.41,0:02:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座小镇里  有着充满了谜团的杀人集团
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.70,0:02:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果在此居住有什么问题的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.57,0:02:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干脆就回旧市好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.58,0:02:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一诚他绝不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.45,0:02:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑且是先给您一个忠告
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.22,0:02:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.50,0:02:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请再给我们一些时间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.03,0:02:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今我们都没有过…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.84,0:02:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你们应该已经知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.89,0:02:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年比较特殊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.80,0:02:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.06,0:02:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我们想一家人一起克服
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.00,0:03:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然您这么说  那好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.63,0:03:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九澄同学  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.56,0:03:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.43,0:03:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.95,0:03:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.41,0:03:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫无变化的早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.17,0:03:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平凡的日常
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.07,0:03:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但总觉得发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.14,0:03:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你惊吓过度了  博士君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.17,0:03:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.94,0:03:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.07,0:03:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我提前来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.72,0:03:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  居然丢下她了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.04,0:03:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃一定生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.24,0:03:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.23,0:03:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀  难道说和小铃吵架了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.46,0:04:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不  没有那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.59,0:04:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  博士君有些地方还是很迟钝的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.32,0:04:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定已经惹小铃生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.81,0:04:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.96,0:04:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  博士君？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.10,0:04:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.09,0:04:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.77,0:04:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.41,0:04:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎你觉得我是个麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.75,0:04:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你的叔父
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.80,0:04:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个中心的栉名田院长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.12,0:04:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说我是个奇怪的人什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.98,0:04:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.70,0:04:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.70,0:04:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  如果有什么话要和我说的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.24,0:05:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.64,0:05:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.65,0:05:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃请假了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.61,0:05:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.87,0:05:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  今天也精神地开始上课吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.37,0:05:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时把一诚关在家里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.97,0:05:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说  我们家人必须做点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.18,0:05:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五十铃也同意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.27,0:05:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.40,0:05:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会变成这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.36,0:05:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.70,0:05:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子说不定要不行了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.09,0:05:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是还有胶囊什么的  一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.13,0:05:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的没错  家人一起克服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.25,0:05:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五十铃  你也要当心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.68,0:05:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.42,0:05:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了  五十铃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.45,0:05:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果连你也有什么事的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.72,0:05:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.88,0:05:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去看看老哥的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.40,0:06:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.67,0:06:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.54,0:06:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥  不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.57,0:06:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.81,0:06:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去拿胶囊来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.84,0:06:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  你也需要的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.22,0:06:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.70,0:06:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联防队那些家伙来过了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.00,0:06:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.15,0:06:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.75,0:06:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.26,0:06:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你们担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.54,0:06:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  之前有说过嫦娥镇流传的都市传说的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.89,0:07:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.07,0:07:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个还有些怎么样的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.41,0:07:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在镇上的食人鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.31,0:07:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,病院的幽灵病房
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.38,0:07:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,排成队伍的红色萤火虫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.48,0:07:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响彻半夜的野兽叫声
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.82,0:07:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这些类似的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.03,0:07:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在镇上的食人鬼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.19,0:07:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.87,0:07:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是这个城镇里住着怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.76,0:07:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们会袭击人这样的传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.56,0:07:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据传闻怪物半夜在镇上徘徊寻找食物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.17,0:07:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在没有人烟的地方袭击人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.06,0:07:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样袭击的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.59,0:07:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是从人的口中直接吸取生气
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.95,0:07:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得像是猎奇电影一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.60,0:07:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我有些事想和你说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.77,0:07:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是一个传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.47,0:07:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都市传说的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.13,0:07:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿着大镰刀的少女吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.31,0:07:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  昨晚真的看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.00,0:08:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个少女袭击人的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.23,0:08:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是想去报警的  但却没有人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.47,0:08:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天早上又去了现场
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.22,0:08:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但事件的痕迹却完全不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.03,0:08:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  拿着大镰刀的少女的传闻什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.99,0:08:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的都市传说听过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.26,0:08:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个没有听说过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.43,0:08:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.47,0:08:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  但是这事听起来挺有趣的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.13,0:08:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为博士君来说  算是不错了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.59,0:08:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不错什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.05,0:08:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然有这样的才能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.05,0:08:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是「有其父必有其子」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.04,0:08:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…这可不是我瞎编的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.66,0:08:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不过还是继续说给我听吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.44,0:08:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好再说说那个拿着大镰刀的少女的角色特点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.17,0:08:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能让故事更有趣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.35,0:08:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.54,0:08:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.67,0:09:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  小铃怎么回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.46,0:09:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她以前都不怎么请假的  小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.60,0:09:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去时我去看望一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.16,0:09:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.10,0:09:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥  吃晚饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.74,0:09:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.50,0:00:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.29,0:10:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  工作有进展吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢  走三步退二步的感觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.02,0:10:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒退怎么行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.36,0:10:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  最近遇到难关了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.78,0:10:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了对了  这里的传说中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.90,0:10:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有关于拿着大镰刀的少女的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.74,0:10:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.50,0:10:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话去问同班同学那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.74,0:10:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要同学是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.10,0:10:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对  小要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.52,0:10:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是她擅长的领域吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.76,0:10:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要同学也说不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.08,0:10:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我更不可能知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.78,0:10:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.01,0:10:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但姑且会调查一下的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.61,0:10:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.19,0:10:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃完了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.46,0:10:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轮到哥哥收拾了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.11,0:10:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  今天不是麻奈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.04,0:10:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前不是替过你一次吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.45,0:10:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  忘记了  是是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.83,0:11:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了寻找1年前遗弃在南极的狗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.33,0:11:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.71,0:11:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还…还活着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.64,0:11:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小太郎  小次郎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.99,0:11:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.77,0:11:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是食物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.31,0:11:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.71,0:11:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面对饥饿的两条猛犬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.41,0:11:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他能活下来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.05,0:11:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电影  结局——南极物语
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.58,0:11:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近日即将公开
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.29,0:11:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看完电影后的用餐可选择离本院徒步1分钟的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.37,0:11:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖啡店  艾特兰泽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.68,0:11:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖啡店  艾  特  兰  泽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.71,0:11:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八朔~ 八朔~ 嫦娥的八朔~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.78,0:12:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酸呀~ 酸呀~ 呀呀呀呀呀~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.00,0:12:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去丢下垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.68,0:12:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一诚前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.25,0:12:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.84,0:12:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是一诚前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.51,0:13:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要干什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.17,0:13:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.05,0:13:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.48,0:13:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是一诚前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.31,0:13:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.14,0:13:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说会从人的口中吸取生气
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.93,0:13:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会被杀的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.63,0:13:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.77,0:14:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.67,0:14:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.00,0:14:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.80,0:14:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为会这样  我们才忠告你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.16,0:15:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.82,0:15:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我  前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.00,0:15:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是谁？  放手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.09,0:15:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你安分点  我们便不会动粗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.25,0:15:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能跟我们走一趟么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.31,0:15:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.90,0:15:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈他呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.20,0:15:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和…  摘花前辈他一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.11,0:15:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.25,0:15:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据戒律  摘花一诚先生他应当很快就会受到制裁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.61,0:15:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且  你也已经不再是迄今为止的那个你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.41,0:15:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么一回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.14,0:15:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.05,0:16:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是爽毙了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.07,0:16:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么爽的事  为什么我一直以来都得忍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.69,0:16:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尝过了这味道  就再也回不去原先的世界了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.23,0:16:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回你个头！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.68,0:16:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坠天之神  除之
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.68,0:16:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(326,434)\fs24}狼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.80,0:16:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥…！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.57,0:17:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一诚前辈他…  怎么了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.49,0:17:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点不太对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.53,0:17:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经有些疯狂了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.16,0:17:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.22,0:17:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样根本就无济于事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.29,0:17:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  那样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.01,0:17:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是眠吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.04,0:17:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.71,0:17:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.80,0:17:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.77,0:17:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联防队町田先生叫我传个话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.61,0:17:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被摘花一诚变成「神人」的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.03,0:17:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石我木雅美  请叔父大人处置
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.71,0:17:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…是么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.76,0:17:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她那边  明天就由我亲自来说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.83,0:17:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.30,0:17:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小眠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.59,0:17:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.67,0:17:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也挺不容易呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.83,0:17:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.04,0:18:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃她  今天也休息么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.89,0:18:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.87,0:18:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说  哥你被她甩了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.66,0:18:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.95,0:18:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩笑  玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.42,0:18:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不走的话  可要迟到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.35,0:18:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.81,0:18:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要去叫下她？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.68,0:18:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是她真不太舒服  还在睡的话  可就打扰她了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.31,0:18:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.48,0:18:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…  太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.85,0:18:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五十铃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.84,0:18:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事已至此  你也别再护着一诚了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.85,0:18:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.98,0:18:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会说出那么冷淡的话？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.07,0:18:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是一家人么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.64,0:18:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了  五十铃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.29,0:18:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不想连你也一并失去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.38,0:18:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.26,0:19:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是戒律
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.26,0:19:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.83,0:19:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胶囊的事应该是机密事项
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.82,0:19:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又是怎么查出来的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.51,0:19:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这世上  知晓消息的人只要超过了一个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.60,0:19:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那便不可能保密
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.36,0:19:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打的是什么算盘？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.15,0:19:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的又是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.51,0:19:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是一早就说了的么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.31,0:19:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想助院长您一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.94,0:19:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  就像你们医生为了解患者的病情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.23,0:19:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要借助病历卡一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.23,0:19:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的新药  也得靠着数据来开发
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.49,0:19:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.22,0:19:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九澄君  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.82,0:19:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.04,0:20:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.09,0:20:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃她呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.75,0:20:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天就没有联系过你么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.80,0:20:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.72,0:20:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她家  你也没去？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.43,0:20:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…  没去成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.03,0:20:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.18,0:20:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是发生了什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.41,0:20:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.15,0:20:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.45,0:20:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也精神地开始上课吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.16,0:20:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  安静
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.85,0:20:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐回座位上去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.67,0:20:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我迟到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.28,0:20:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  摘花  正好迟到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.96,0:20:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.31,0:20:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃  真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.01,0:20:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可让我担心了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.54,0:20:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.97,0:20:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  就先点名吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.51,0:21:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.41,0:21:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…  感冒好了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.70,0:21:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.58,0:21:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…  昨天是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.12,0:21:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.36,0:21:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了什么事么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.00,0:21:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥他…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.06,0:21:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.04,0:21:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥他…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.19,0:21:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搬家了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.78,0:21:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.14,0:21:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.76,0:21:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一诚前辈他搬家了…  这…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.31,0:22:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…  小铃…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.38,0:22:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥他被杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.56,0:22:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.37,0:23:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六心乱极
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.11,0:23:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铃若闇虚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.11,0:23:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退魔之力
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.29,0:23:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八朔香里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.75,0:23:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,望镇邪气
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.28,0:24:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那未曾被我接受的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.74,0:24:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那难以令我理解的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.71,0:24:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么办…  怎么做…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.10,0:24:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到头来  我还是什么也办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.61,0:24:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  恋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
